 +  where 3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280>([18])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280> = [[1, 18], [1, 18, 1], [18], [18, 1], [1, 18], [1, 18, 1], ...].count
 +  and   3 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280>([1, 18])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280> = [[1, 18], [1, 18, 1], [18], [18, 1], [1, 18], [1, 18, 1], ...].count
 +  and   2 = <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280>([18, 1])
 +    where <built-in method count of list object at 0x74c251e22280> = [[1, 18], [1, 18, 1], [18], [18, 1], [1, 18], [1, 18, 1], ...].count
